:set nu
:set tabstop=3
:set shiftwidth=3
:set expandtab
syntax on

"The space bar under normal mode does nothing, so make full use of it
:map <space>q :q<CR>
:map <space><space> :!
:map <space>w :w<CR>


"disable arrow keys what so ever,
:map <up> <Esc>
:map <down> <Esc>
:map <left> <Esc>
:map <right> <Esc>
:vmap <up> <Esc>
:vmap <down> <Esc>
:vmap <left> <Esc>
:vmap <right> <Esc>
:imap <up> <Esc>
:imap <down> <Esc>
:imap <left> <Esc>
:imap <right> <Esc>
